title: Thunderf00t vs Richard Carrier (Devil's Advocate Amongst Atheists?)
description:
Atheist vs. atheist; here's my response to a long-simmering dispute between two public intellectuals from opposite ends of the academic spectrum… but, wait, who are you calling an academic anyway?

Link to Richard Carrier videos: http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgTHJb93koSgIXieStJD-Kw
Link to Thunderf00t videos: http://www.youtube.com/user/Thunderf00t/playlists

Link to the specific quotation from Thunderf00t mentioned: http://youtu.be/inqcLXNlEes?t=18m27s
